Awp_abstract_b1
Made by: kaos4u
Date: 4/11/08
Player spawn points: 32
Filesize: 4.48 MB  (All custome textures, sounds,skybox, and .nav is packed in the .bsp)
Contact info: kaos4u@gmail.com
========================
Custome skybox made by: Karatekafer
Custom texture art made by: NEone
Other custome content made by: kaos4u (textures and sounds)
========================
This map is an AWO map.  All players spawn with AWP, knife, and Nightvision.  There is a button at the top of the map that dynamicly changes every round.  It does one of three things:
1- Teleports all alive players to a knife arena (strips all players of all weapons and equips a knife.)  Th arena is set on snow and slippery ice.
2- Chnages server gravity for the round and plays the benny hill chase song.
3- ???  You get cake! :)
This is a beta version.  Please feel free to midify as you wish (Don't forget to credit, where is due.)  FYI, the button is a little bit buggy you may have to press it a few times to get it to work.
